  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the effect of hand massage, switched on diathermy or sham/switched off
      diathermy on DOMS in a group of athletes suffering DOMS after a ski mountaineering race.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study examine DOMS in athletes following a ski mountaineering race, pain measured with
      numbering pain rating scale NPRS and perceived global improvement (PGIC) after treatment have
      been measured after a massage treatment, a diathermy treatment and a sham diathermy
      treatment.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
